This is a device that generates a thick cloud of nanobots, providing its user with mobile Partial Cover. 

{{image | name=nanoscreen0.jpg | style=128 }}

{{skillbox |black| NANOSCREEN | AUTOMATIC EQUIPMENT }}
{{skill-label | Obligatory }}
{{effects}}
* In game terms, a Nanoscreen provides its user with 360&deg; Partial Cover, providing the Trooper with the corresponding [[MODs]] for [[Partial Cover]], which '''cannot''' be added to other Cover MODs. 
* To represent the Nanoscreen, the player must place a Nanoscreen Token in [[Silhouette]] contact with the user. 
* This device cannot be used against [[CC Attacks]].





